decision_details:
- the proposal made by Hon. Dinesh Gunawardena, Minister of Water Supply and Drainage, to revise the total Estimated Cost of the following seven water supply projects, due to the change of the original scope of work and also due to price escalations, was approved by the Cabinet:

		*	Jaltara-Ranala Water Supply Project;
		*	Embilipitiya Water Supply Project;
		*	Medirigiriya Water Supply Project;
		*	Kundasale Water Supply Project;
		*	Matale Water Supply Project;
		*	Marassana Water Supply Project; and
		*	Thalawakale Water Supply Project.
